Reply  Re: Leveling 16 to 24
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 I just wanted to agree about fighting in Highpass. I jumped from lvl 14 to lvl 17 in under 2 days, moderate playing. 17-19 there was a little slower, but the PP was great. total i probably made 300-400PP from 14-19. at 19 i tried Highhold, but got bored so went to fight aviaks in SK. been there ever since, i am 21 now.

Dialdar Solarflarez <Sacred Alliances>
21st lvl Human Druid on Cazic-Thule 
 
