Reply  bub an hour
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 To keep that momentum going from 25 to 30 head to Cazic Thule. Bad train city, but once you are in the right group in the Throne room, Gators or 4C, exp is mad. Bub an or less in TR, non stop mayhem. Gonne solo till 33 then I will hit solb, more crazy exp.

Good luck

Sabena 27th druid (22hours played)
Teraos Fiochmhar 50th SK 
 
Fuzzyfoot07
Registered User
(5/16/01 12:19:04 pm)
Reply  Re: bub an hour
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 At lvl 22 I headed for Everfrost and killed Wolly Mammoths. Started kiting Friday night at about 1am no one was there. I leveled in about 4-5 hours there and the tusks that drop sell for 7-8pp each. Nice pp and really nice XP. I did this really until lvl 29 with just leaving a few times. Sure after lvl 25-26 you can get better XP somewhere else but the Tusks were just nice to sell at that level.

Fuzzyfoot Jollymeade
52 Druid
Soul Cadre
Torv. Server  

